==English==

===Noun===
'''gully'''
#{{cricket}} A [[fielding]] [[position]] on the [[off]] [[side]] about 30 [[degree]]s behind [[square]], between the [[slip]]s and [[point]]; a [[fielder]] in such a position
#(United Kingdom) A [[drop kerb]]
#(United States of America) A landform created by running water eroding sharply into a hillside
#A [[sailor|sailor's]] pocket [[knife]]
#*'''1883''', [[w:Robert Louis Stevenson|Robert Louis Stevenson]], ''[[w:Treasure Island|Treasure Island]]''
#*: With that I made my mind up, took out my '''gully''', opened it with my teeth, and cut one strand after another...

